flowchart TD
    PDF[PDF File] --> CLI[CLI / Config]
    CLI --> LOOP[For each page]

    LOOP --> EXT[Extract text\nPyMuPDF]
    LOOP --> RENDER[Render page\nto PNG base64]

    EXT --> CLASSIFY[analyze_page\nclassify content]
    RENDER --> CLASSIFY

    CLASSIFY --> T{PageType?}

    T -->|EMPTY| SKIP[Skip — blank page]
    T -->|TEXT| TS[text_strategy\nprompt: text]
    T -->|FORMULA| IS1[image_strategy\nprompt: formula]
    T -->|IMAGE| IS2[image_strategy\nprompt: diagram]
    T -->|MIXED| IS3[image_strategy\nprompt: default]

    TS --> LLM[LM Studio\nLocal LLM]
    IS1 --> LLM
    IS2 --> LLM
    IS3 --> LLM

    LLM --> RES[ConversionResult\nmarkdown + timing + tokens]
    SKIP --> RES

    RES --> POST[Postprocess\ncombine pages]
    POST --> OUT[Markdown output file]
